        "subject": "LU-3687 tests: use test_mkdir() -p options to create $tdir",
        "message": "LU-3687 tests: use test_mkdir() -p options to create $tdir\n\ntest_mkdir() creates parent directory only if called with\n-p option. Several tests are failed if run separately\nbecause of parent directory d0.sanity does not exist.\n\nPatch adds test_mkdir() -p option to the tests which create\n$tdir.\n\nSigned-off-by: Elena Gryaznova <elena_gryaznova@xyratex.com>\nXyratex-bug-id: MRP-1194\nChange-Id: Ifd70ce631cc6a0ff1fd4a5ebe27ef47e1e6d17f0\n"
      },
